    "title": "Lead Investment Banker at Sharekhan Global Group",
    "description": "Sharekhan Global Group invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Investment Banker at our Srinagar location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Sharekhan Global Group:\nSharekhan Global Group is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in VBA\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sharekhan Global Group!",
